    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "Intricate",
      "uuid": "5d1ca85246b84c9faae64a1abe8463c1",
      "x": 11063.116545102426,
      "y": 7501.760613219063,
      "width": 454.4683664288025,
      "height": 136.0,
      "z_value": -9.96400000000002,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "This is really when she started changing her own approach\nNoticing how each of them took absolute command from their own peers\nWithin their relative tiers"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "about",
      "title": "Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot",
      "uuid": "2fbeb742fc97451198e9f0f6bf4b6de8",
      "x": 5860.90701567654,
      "y": 2581.150943148832,
      "width": 468.0,
      "height": 29.0,
      "z_value": -9.65700000000019,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": false,
      "label": "Left foot, right foot, left foot, right foot",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": ""
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "claude_response",
      "title": "Response",
      "uuid": "d8e1659287654292996c521658684ced",
      "x": 22319.540612609962,
      "y": -533.9713501868982,
      "width": 420.0,
      "height": 288.0,
      "z_value": -10.0,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "label": "The `emoji` field stays on the dataclass (so the node can read it at paint time) but never enters `to_dict()` and is never read from `from_dict()`. Every app launch, every node gets a fresh roll from the pool. The graph breathes.",
      "depth_front": false,
      "node_tint": "#5a6a5a"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "d69be5bbe4b74940a849c2c37b38090f",
      "x": 50825.80567920619,
      "y": 26869.24371439642,
      "width": 316.89878873709677,
      "height": 282.8608372212002,
      "z_value": -9.447000000000306,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "And the funny part you noticed has a sharper edge to it: they're moving toward the very state they're trying to flee from. They see \"slow\" or \"quiet\" as the failure mode and sprint away from it, but slow and quiet was the low-entropy state. They're running from order toward disorder while perceiving themselves to be running from disorder toward order, because their orientation got inverted somewhere in the misreading of the visible output. The vacuum looked like the failure they wanted to escape, so they escaped it, and in escaping it they accelerated toward the actual failure they were ostensibly trying to prevent. Pure cosmic irony, made mandatory by physics."
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "fca77c24dd06489ca0272666473ded08",
      "x": 49450.98235778654,
      "y": 25378.63516616209,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 200.0,
      "z_value": -9.464000000000297,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "Historical population growth \u2014 actual vs. potential per context\nPrimary goods and services \u2014 future demand vs. peak vs. supply chain throughput\nTop 10 destination hotshots + handling time per hub\nChain practices per link/node along the full route\nPhase 1 reasoning chain \u2014 modular per-node application with timing, gain/effort, risk mitigation, and macroeconomic singleton multiplier as the qualifying gate\nOrigin and operational layer (this conversation):"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "warm",
      "title": "",
      "uuid": "cb4d7ed9b3114b8f8edd86e147627842",
      "x": 48692.819748622554,
      "y": 25255.833121726588,
      "width": 300.0,
      "height": 200.0,
      "z_value": -9.462000000000298,
      "ports_visible": false,
      "shelf_visible": true,
      "body_text": "You said: \"same principle at every scale\"\n\"same principle at every scale\"\n-space rocket spends most of its life cycle not going fast at all until you light it up\n-Usain bolt isn't fast at all while going to 7-11, until it comes time to race"
    },
    {
      "node_id": 0,
      "node_type": "image",
      "title": "Image",
