      "label": "This works quite fine\nSure some people would just\nAdd a font selector to a node\n\nBut we went ahead \nAnd created a text node\nFor the Lato font writing \nAnd an About node \nFor the chandler42 writing,\n\nNo no sir we no be clicking and licking\nThings we are not supposed to.",
